Paper: hep-th/9408056

Date: 1994-08-09

Title: Anyonic FRT construction

Authors: Shahn Majid and M.J. Rodriguez-Plaza

Comments: 11 pages, Latex, DAMTP/94-64, NIKHEF-H 94-25

The Faddeev-Reshetikhin-Takhtajan method to construct matrix bialgebras fromnon-singular solutions of the quantum Yang-Baxter equation is extended to theanyonic or $\Z_n$-graded case. The resulting anyonic quantum matrices arebraided groups in which the braiding is given by a phase factor.